manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Makes a Great Gift Kids and toddlers love this fun airplane toy set and will love you for it! It comes in a nice box and is a present you can be proud to give. Kids love to drive 'em, fly 'em and push 'em!

Fun Airplane Toy Set for Young Children Made with strong, durable material, this fun toy aircraft plane pack comes with 4 planes on wheels - 2 vintage and 2 modern - in bright kid friendly colors - red, orange, blue, and yellow. These planes are the perfect size for little hands and easy to grip for toddlers and kids. These top toys for boys and girls are popular with kids and make the best gifts.

Play Time is All the Time Each fun plastic plane toy is easy to grip, which makes them fun to play with for young kids. Children love them. Going on a plane or road trip? These airplane toys make traveling by airplane or car better and easier for your child AND you!

Provides Hours of Fun For Kids on the Go This fun airplane car set keeps kids happy and occupied wherever they happen to be: airport, car, restaurant, or home. Well Made and Durable This quality play set can stand up to the rough and tough play kids can dish out. Helps Kids Imaginations Fly These fun airplanes can help kids imaginations soar them high in the sky!

Make a Little Kid Happy Looking for a great birthday gift, Christmas present or 'just because' toy for a boy or girl in your life? Want to give them a fun toy they will play with again and again? Want a gift that you will feel good about giving? This fun airplane toy set is for you!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 1, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, colorful, easy for little hands to fly around!
reviews.reviewText: I ordered these because we had a birthday party for a 4 year old and I wanted a little gift for the other children attending. I opened the box and put one in each of the 4 other children's little gift bag, they were thrilled to have them. They range in age from 2 to 4 and besides flying them around they also wound them up on the floor and had races. These are as cute as can be and I am sure they will last a long time.

reviews.reviewText: The little airplanes from 3 Bees and Me arrived quickly and in great shape. It is such an adorable gift for a little one and will provide hours of fun and entertainment. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 7, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Great little planes. Durable, harder plastic so younger kids won't be able to chew off pieces 😅 They're also pull-back type toys. Some reviews complained they got different colors than pictured but the ones we received are the ones in the photo.
